<th colspan="2" style="text-align:center; font-size:larger;" class="fn summary">Washington Irving</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align:center;" class=""><a href="/wiki/File:Irving-Washington-LOC.jpg" class="image" title="Irving-Washington-LOC.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bf/Irving-Washington-LOC.jpg/200px-Irving-Washington-LOC.jpg" width="200" height="285" border="0" /></a><br />
<small><a href="/wiki/Daguerreotype" title="Daguerreotype">Daguerreotype</a> of Washington Irving taken by <a href="/w/index.php?title=John_Plumbe&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="John Plumbe (page does not exist)">John Plumbe</a> and later copied by <a href="/wiki/Mathew_Brady" title="Mathew Brady">Mathew Brady</a></small></td>
</tr>
<tr>
