<li>Grant, John. (2006) <i>Discarded Science: Ideas that seemed good at the time ...</i> [sic], ff&amp;f (Facts, Figures &amp; Fun), publisher, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781904332497" class="internal">ISBN 978-1-904332-49-7</a> hardcover.</li>
